sub_title: Full Stack Developer | Backend Developer | PHP JavaScript SQL
summary: Enthusiastic BSc in Information Technology at InHolland University student and 4-year software engineering course graduate at International IT Academy with 5 years’ of academic and professional experience in software engineering, full-stack development, graphic design, project management and information security. Track record in guiding product development life-cycle from conception to implementation for various projects, including iOS and Android mobile applications and games, desktop, web and database applications. Highly experienced in planning and designing software solutions. Competent in understanding design patterns and Object Oriented Programming, proficient in JavaScript, PHP and SQL. Fluent in Russian, English and Azerbaijani, intermediate in Turkish and beginner in Dutch.
